    "columns": 1,
    "content": "\u003cp\u003eTo obtain a challenging position as a Software Development Engineer (SDE) or Machine Learning Engineer, where I can apply my strong programming skills and deep understanding of AI, computer vision, and data-driven solutions to solve complex Problems. I am eager to contribute to innovative projects that combine robust software engineering with advanced machine learning techniques, while continuously learning and growing as a technology professional. I am a Fast learner with a self-driven, high-ownership mindset, experienced in quickly mastering new tools, products, and technologies to meet customer requirement. I am skilled in relationship building, follow-ups, technical support, and long-term account retention, ensuring both pre-sales and post-sales success. I am Competitive and target-oriented, with demonstrated discipline through independent project execution, deadline ownership, and continuous upskilling in advanced engineering domains.\u003c/p\u003e",
